==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# Someone who [[guard]]s, [[watch]]es over, or [[protect]]s.
# {{law}} One who is [[legally]] [[responsible]] for the [[care]] and [[management]] of the [[person]] or [[property]] of an [[incompetent]] or [[minor]].
# A [[superior]] in a [[Franciscan]] [[monastery]].

